OL,3,CWorld-first gene-editing therapy for
OL,4,Cblood disorders approved for NHS use
OL,6,FThe new treatment offers those who
OL,7,Fsuffer from a life-limiting blood
OL,8,Fdisorder a chance to live without
OL,9,Fneeding regular blood transfusions
OL,11,FHundreds of people in England with a
OL,12,Flife-limiting blood disorder are set
OL,13,Fto benefit from a world-first gene-
OL,14,Fediting therapy after it was given the
OL,15,Fgreen light for NHS use.
OL,17,FHealth bosses hailed the decision by
OL,18,Fthe National Institute for Health and
OL,19,FCare Excellence (NICE) as a "historic
OL,20,Fmoment" for patients with the
OL,21,Fcondition.
