OL,3,CWorld-first gene-editing therapy for
OL,4,Cblood disorders approved for NHS use
OL,6,FIt was developed through a partnership
OL,7,Fbetween Vertex Pharmaceuticals and
OL,8,FCrispr Therapeutics and is licensed
OL,9,Fusing the gene-editing tool Crispr -
OL,10,Ftechnology which earned its inventors
OL,11,Fthe Nobel Prize for chemistry in 2020.
OL,13,FAccording to the Nice guidance, the
OL,14,Flist price for a course of Casgevy is
OL,15,F#1.65 million. However, it is
OL,16,Favailable to the NHS at a discount due
OL,17,Fto a commercial agreement with the
OL,18,Fhealth service. It will be funded
OL,19,Fimmediately and rolled out to up to
OL,20,F460 eligible patients.
