OL,11,FAmanda Pritchard, NHS England chief
OL,12,Fexecutive, said: "Ordinarily, patients
OL,13,Fexperience painful side effects and
OL,14,Fundergo regular transfusions which
OL,15,Fseverely impact their quality of life,
OL,16,Fbut this therapy offers people a life
OL,17,Ffree from that as well as the hope of
OL,18,Fliving longer, which is truly amazing
OL,19,Fnews.
