OL,3,CWorld-first gene-editing therapy for
OL,4,Cblood disorders approved for NHS use
OL,6,F"This is the latest in a series of
OL,7,Frevolutionary gene therapies to be
OL,8,Fsecured by NHS England over the past
OL,9,Ffive years, bringing significant
OL,10,Fbenefit for patients."
OL,12,FHelen Knight, director of medicines
OL,13,Fevaluation at NICE, added: "Although
OL,14,Fthere are some uncertainties in the
OL,15,Fevidence for its long-term benefits,
OL,16,Fthe committee felt (Casgevy) could
OL,17,Frepresent a potential cure for some
OL,18,Fpeople with TDT."
