OL,4,Cblood disorders approved for NHS use
OL,6,FKirthana Balachandran, 21, from West
OL,7,FLondon, was diagnosed with TDT when
OL,8,Fshe was three months old.
OL,10,FThe medical student said: "I
OL,11,Fconstantly worry about the future and
OL,12,Fwhat blood transfusions would be like
OL,13,Fwhen I'm older and how I will manage
OL,14,Fmy condition. With gene therapy, I
OL,15,Fwouldn't have to worry about the side
OL,16,Feffects of blood transfusions and the
OL,17,Freactions I could have, such as iron
OL,18,Fdepositing in my heart and liver."
